title: Does tensorflow support mfcc now?
body_html:
Is mfcc support in tensorflow now? I found this https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/core/kernels/mfcc.h

but I can't find this op in Python API in tensorflow.

So is that not open yet? Or it's wrapped in some other Python api?
